proxs3 (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Multipart upload support for files >5GB (AWS SDK upload manager)
  * Prevent uploading partial writes (fileInUse /proc/fd check, skip .tmp files)
  * Per-storage cache-max-age property for automatic local cache eviction
  * Cache metadata in .meta/ subdirectory (fixes watcher sidecar loop)
  * activate_volume downloads S3 objects on demand
  * Graceful degradation when S3 is unreachable (timeouts, stale cache serving)
  * Endpoint config sanitisation (strip protocol prefix and trailing slash)
  * Credentials optional for public buckets

